messages.message: Hi team, there was 2 feature requests at todays AI Hub for enterprise enablement session
1. Prompt Suggestion from @cooper.addis - Could we get a prompt suggester feature? Certain starter prompts will give different eg: give the value of x vs what is the x

2. Multiple Languages options from @cooper.addis - Can we add a language selector on AIhub? I have a few prospects that wouldnâ€™t use the website simply because the apps are all US and UK focussed (we just need to translate the language, not remake all the apps)
